{"tid":279004,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［短篇真人真事］在瑞士遇上她","createTime":"2017-06-11T01:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T04:22:15.000Z","uid":17569,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de31102bc6dfeb5708c4b2478b504cdeaedbff9f","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"半年前我去歐洲backpack<br />\n途中瑞士hostel遇上佢<br />\n佢黎自中國東北，但就去左荷蘭讀書<br />\n畢業準備搵工前特登去瑞士玩下<br />\n我地一齊玩左3日 去左唔同既雪山<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/151913_c28745199f58339821a7e5e351207e91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F151913_c28745199f58339821a7e5e351207e91.jpg&h=448e4c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後一日大家坐左起湖邊傾心事<br />\n我用我好爛既普通話再加英文同佢溝通<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/151604_81525b8e6918b7504d8c5cea77f1878c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F151604_81525b8e6918b7504d8c5cea77f1878c.jpg&h=21d236b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我繼續我既旅程 佢亦都要返荷蘭"},{"pid":"d6ef2b30ab0157941eb7fcddfe1304286ca95d98","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n佢係一個大中華膠 <br />\n最後一晚起hostel common room 同佢一路食晚飯一路討論政治<br />\n我話有部分香港人其實唔鐘意內地人<br />\n佢竟然眼紅 然後流左幾滴馬尿<br />\n我凝視住佢 覺得佢有幾分單純、可愛<br />\n<br />\n第二朝離別時我送上一個水晶球<br />\n水晶球底部寫上<br />\n&quot;就讓這三天的回憶永遠存活於水晶球裏<br />\n25-11-2016&quot;<br />\n我自己亦買左一個同款水晶球<br />\n去為呢段回憶留下印記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/005623_196b12b7d8de1179b626036abce7fc2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F005623_196b12b7d8de1179b626036abce7fc2e.jpg&h=af15da65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水晶球為瑞士少女峰 <br />\n亦即是我地第二日去過既地方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錯的時空；對的人，<br />\n到底掩沒了多少緣份？"},{"pid":"d1e856d6416b7a554c0f283001b8a6ee7b678696","tid":279004,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開唔開始到"},{"pid":"dfc8e921a083e03f97cc5ff9d30c473346aba938","tid":279004,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c8d8a8022a5195ccd33294cba26cb4e68126d0c","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"#3<br />\n之後我去左其他歐洲國家<br />\n但仍然放唔低佢<br />\nThe best thing about being a backpacker is that you can change your plan at anytime<br />\n所以我做左一個決定....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/011508_c635b4b15d6f4ab4ed68740df9968280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F011508_c635b4b15d6f4ab4ed68740df9968280.jpg&h=70bc9e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買機票飛去荷蘭玩多三日先返香港<br />\n佢亦都好開心 話會做我既導遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇見一個月終於讓我再次遇上佢<br />\n我地第一日去左風車村 但天氣好差<br />\n大家都冇乜引 唯一好笑既係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/094416_ddee1480da84236edb481a4ea3e66a14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F094416_ddee1480da84236edb481a4ea3e66a14.jpg&h=d6af3bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風車村啲鴨以為我對鞋係麵包<br />\n跟住我起勢咁啄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日去左啤酒博物館參觀<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/094713_80bd42af1f6ad0d41fd7f765668b1089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F094713_80bd42af1f6ad0d41fd7f765668b1089.jpg&h=f33295f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入場時佢會比一條手帶你<br />\n條手帶有3粒紐 <br />\n一粒紐可以換一杯酒黎飲<br />\n又或者用2粒去玩佢啲活動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢走左去學點做bartender<br />\n點斟酒 最後有張證書拎<br />\n話你係一個qualified bartender<br />\n我就寧願拎哂黎飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/012707_cf21cef3777086750486642cf8c5ce72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F012707_cf21cef3777086750486642cf8c5ce72.jpg&h=d191ab5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n酒過三巡 佢面紅個樣更加令人憐愛"},{"pid":"9264975f7a19a59bd6bcec27ee9ce44f9bee71ff","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"#4<br />\n果晚佢無啦啦帶左我去唐人街買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來佢話佢準備左煮吉野家牛肉飯比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話佢記得我曾經同佢講過 我食西餐食到好厭<br />\n其實我都唔撚記得自己講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果晚我地買完餸就返去hostel<br />\n起個廚房到一齊煮飯<br />\nLike a cute couple<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/165726_cefef1473ab4f7dd40227ef823300d5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F165726_cefef1473ab4f7dd40227ef823300d5a.jpg&h=d91e4a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成品<br />\n佢煮得真係幾好<br />\n啲牛肉醃到好入味<br />\n同埋佢知我唔食洋蔥 <br />\n影完相之後再逐一幫我夾返走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果晚我真係完全敗於佢裙下"},{"pid":"39443cdd97ebbd3962c8c6f6f6493a152ed4ff61","tid":279004,"uid":111081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"兩隻都係男人既手。。。"},{"pid":"9463b91fda7292c440e8b21cee4bfecddbdfe0e8","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:12:40.000Z","msg":"#5<br />\n第三日我同佢去左海牙玩<br />\n黃昏時間於海邊漫步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/184513_ab75594949c3e1ee8807ae1032fe3c5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F184513_ab75594949c3e1ee8807ae1032fe3c5e.jpg&h=35cbc26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫柔既海浪聲源源不絕<br />\n再加上海風緩緩吹拂<br />\n整個畫面變得有詩意起來<br />\n我地就起呢個畫面入面談天說笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我倆亦慢慢接近對方<br />\n佢伸出右手挽住我手臂<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/185402_7e08ac1a48c86cc2db8b180d2ea31369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F185402_7e08ac1a48c86cc2db8b180d2ea31369.jpg&h=2dde81e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張圖係有人幫我地影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天色漸黑<br />\n我地向前走上燈塔（上面第一幅圖有）<br />\n燈塔既樓梯係有空隙<br />\n同埋用木板做 望落唔穩陣<br />\n好似下圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/185801_cb4cd9de1b1f9649cd75a60a44b97521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F185801_cb4cd9de1b1f9649cd75a60a44b97521.jpg&h=8cfb2641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知佢有畏高 要轉上4層樓梯<br />\n我當然玩下佢 起佢隔離跳黎跳去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就勁驚 攬到條柱實一實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我玩夠之後當然不失風度<br />\n伸隻手出黎扶住佢上樓梯啦<br />\n點知佢一手拖左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我靜係記得我當時心跳好快<br />\n腦海真係一片空白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地就拖住大家一齊登上燈塔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/190410_6b91508b626ab6fe0a11039255add0e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F190410_6b91508b626ab6fe0a11039255add0e3.jpg&h=23f4b7b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一列金黃色的燈光沿著海邊伸展<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/190109_ca58fff06b9aa9ac86e87174382cef29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F10%2F190109_ca58fff06b9aa9ac86e87174382cef29.jpg&h=98fb7b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入夜後，夜景更為迷人"},{"pid":"e1fe937982234bc4a62a7705ea26efd6b92ca0d4","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"#6<br />\n其實我呢兩晚都有送佢返屋企<br />\n當然今晚都唔例外<br />\n但唯一唔同既係我地拖住大家<br />\n走過一條又一條漆黑既街道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚我地異常沈寂<br />\n大概係因為我聽日就要返香港<br />\n大家只想靜靜地 享受尚餘既時間<br />\n道別時 我鼓起勇氣 錫左佢臉頰一下<br />\n佢即刻用一個責備但又冧冧地既眼神望住我<br />\n然後就回頭上樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n責備係因為我地根本冇可能<br />\n何必要為呢段感情增添枝節？<br />\n冧係因為我地都無法否認對大家既感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我約左佢聽日晏就hostel等<br />\n我話我有野準備比佢"},{"pid":"4bbf69517ba9e764901396f83911954044b63d56","tid":279004,"uid":42562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"背影好襯呀，希望你地開始到。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我都好想去荷蘭讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7086963b042170b18a19be66672fa10d5f68a99","tid":279004,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"高妹？"},{"pid":"968a782980c96ee1b62159052960c5da30b94b42","tid":279004,"uid":38874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64e879ac42e2f641d961e90878681c36eaa2ee2a","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"#7<br />\n一大清早我去左唐人街買餸<br />\n其實我係準備走前煮返餐比佢食<br />\n比個surprise 佢之餘<br />\n亦為我地段回憶畫上完美句號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家去過Amsterdam就知<br />\n果到仲有條街係賣花<br />\n我買完所需食材後<br />\n再特登兜去果到買左扎花<br />\n準備走時送比佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢黎到 我已經煮好哂兩樣餸<br />\n同埋滾好湯 放左起餐枱到<br />\n默默等佢到來  <br />\n佢黎到時 表現得好驚喜<br />\n唔係因為我煮野比佢食<br />\n而係原來佢今朝又係起屋企煮好飯 <br />\n放左入暖壺 拎左過黎<br />\n同我一樣諗法 想煮最後一餐比對方食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我叫佢果啲留返今晚自己食<br />\n食左我煮果啲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/200359_dd46b2b6490dac9c9fc224d743ff4011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F200359_dd46b2b6490dac9c9fc224d743ff4011.jpg&h=496f3f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩餸一湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 啲飯我都係起China Town現成買"},{"pid":"2d2adb10b5d40af652bd2c6e8ae55eb0725046c1","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"#8<br />\n飯後我地出發去機場<br />\nCheck in後我起袋入面拎左扎花出黎送比佢<br />\n唔知呢個係女仔指定動作定點<br />\n收花後好鐘意哄埋去聞<br />\n當然啦 由於我札花太平 我聞過係冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但望住佢起勢咁聞 又覺得佢好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢亦都準備左一樣禮物比我<br />\n我打開一睇 係一條領呔<br />\n佢話佢希望我可以戴住佢見工<br />\n起香港搵到一份好工 好好為未來打算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離境前我同佢相擁超過1分鐘<br />\n正式離別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭飛機時我睇返我同佢影過既相<br />\n片片絲絲既回憶不斷湧現<br />\n抑壓住既情感我一下子爆發<br />\n係我個半月backpack旅程入面<br />\n第一次流淚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/202800_864ddf1729de103c0a7a17f4686079bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F202800_864ddf1729de103c0a7a17f4686079bd.jpg&h=64552105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張相係我為佢影<br />\n亦係我最鐘意既一張"},{"pid":"bfb90dc68eade43805d9e505498fff09787d570c","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"#後記<br />\n要造就一段愛情，<br />\n「緣份」二字缺一不可。<br />\n有緣有份可成夫妻；<br />\n有緣無份便成過客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對的人，錯的時間；<br />\n錯的人；對的時間，<br />\n都足以掩沒一段感情。<br />\n人生上的過客有很多，<br />\n希望<br />\n剛失戀的人，看到這裡，能夠釋懷，<br />\n剛熱戀的人，看到這裡，能夠珍惜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捉不到的愛情放在心裡已很足夠。<br />\n「感激車站裹，尚有月台能讓我們滿足到落淚。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"7c534580761ac78c2d09f6603b4a4c33cbd10842","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高妹？</blockquote><br />\n唔高 係佢對鞋個跟比較高"},{"pid":"48bbcb2171f7169ab244e3920b08fbc17dc23658","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背影好襯呀，希望你地開始到。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我都好想去荷蘭讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住 令你失望了"},{"pid":"cceae43cd9033efa875bbc9952d66abd6e6b0aa6","tid":279004,"uid":11736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:53:18.000Z","msg":"歐洲版目黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2de2b32db8fae0ac5c9bf856add5dbabfccbc0","tid":279004,"uid":86275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"真係好短帶佢返香港啦"},{"pid":"398bf2cf320c3bca6925c1713ecc65131efd5bed","tid":279004,"uid":48889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"仲有冇聯絡"},{"pid":"6a9ca54503cc6ef36aa88591292d8ca581eddc03","tid":279004,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"娶咗佢啦 會抱憾終生架"},{"pid":"1d61b16e03aa4798e6cd34bb7e085b8edc37d2a4","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有冇聯絡</blockquote><br />\nWechat已甚少聯絡<br />\n佢起荷蘭已經搵到工<br />\n大家各有各忙"},{"pid":"1cd88bfcd7fd0d0f076032c92a5c9254f3491073","tid":279004,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>娶咗佢啦 會抱憾終生架</blockquote><br />\n感覺唔係一切<br />\n我自問未有能力去咁做"},{"pid":"e176da45ccc39956872a19cd6b00b65acde820e6","tid":279004,"uid":38874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9632ef0dd7f12b628d27adf89ba509655e5fcc3","tid":279004,"uid":63037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"個感想結語好傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實點解冇可能一齊？"}]}